== 1. Main Hardware Components

=== Core System Components

==== 1.1 Delta XS Robot

- **Function**: Primary mechanical manipulation system
- **Components Included**:
  - 3-axis delta mechanism
  - Servo motors with encoders
  - End effector/gripper
  - Control board
  - Power supply

==== 1.2 Vision System

- **RGB Color Camera**: For fruit/vegetable color detection
- **Lighting System**: Consistent illumination for color accuracy

==== 1.3 Computing Platform

- **Microcontroller/SBC**: For robot control and image processing
- **Options**: Raspberry Pi 4, Arduino with ESP32, or industrial PC

==== 1.4 Communication Infrastructure

- **Router/Network Equipment**: For API communication and remote monitoring
- **Cables**: Ethernet, USB, power cables

==== 1.5 Mechanical Support Components

- **Conveyor System**: For item feeding (optional)
- **Sorting Bins**: Collection containers for sorted items
- **Mounting Hardware**: Camera mounts, protective enclosures

==== 1.6 Sensors

- **Proximity Sensors**: Object detection
- **Position Encoders**: Already integrated in Delta XS
- **Emergency Stop**: Safety system

