== 4. API Integration Requirements

=== 4.1 Robot Control API
`# Example API endpoints for Delta XS control
POST /api/robot/move
{
    "x": 100,
    "y": 150,
    "z": 50,
    "speed": 80
}

GET /api/robot/status
POST /api/robot/home
POST /api/robot/gripper/open
POST /api/robot/gripper/close
`
=== 4.2 Monitoring API
`# System monitoring endpoints
GET /api/system/health
POST /api/sorting/log
{
    "item_color": "red",
    "bin_location": "bin_1",
    "timestamp": "2025-01-20T10:30:00Z",
    "confidence": 0.95
}

GET /api/statistics/daily
GET /api/camera/capture
`
== 5. Software Architecture

=== 5.1 Main Application Components

- **Color Detection Module**: OpenCV-based color classification
- **Robot Control Interface**: Delta XS communication protocol
- **API Client**: RESTful API communication
- **Web Dashboard**: Real-time monitoring interface
- **Database**: Sorting statistics and logs

=== 5.2 Required Libraries/Frameworks

- OpenCV for image processing
- Flask/FastAPI for web services
- Requests for API communication
- SQLite for data storage
- GPIO libraries for sensor interfacing

== 6. Implementation Plan

=== Phase 1: Hardware Setup

- Install and configure Raspberry Pi
- Mount camera and lighting system
- Connect sensors and emergency stop
- Network configuration

=== Phase 2: Software Development

- Develop color detection algorithm
- Implement robot control interface
- Create API integration layer
- Build monitoring dashboard

=== Phase 3: Integration Testing

- Calibrate color detection system
- Test robot movement accuracy
- Validate API communication
- Performance optimization

=== Phase 4: Deployment

- System documentation
- User training materials
- Maintenance procedures
- Performance monitoring setup

== 7. Safety Considerations

- Emergency stop accessible at all times
- Protective barriers around robot workspace
- Proper grounding of electrical components
- Regular calibration of safety sensors
- Clear operational procedures and training

== 8. Success Metrics

- **Sorting Accuracy**: >95% color classification accuracy
- **Throughput**: Minimum 10 items per minute
- **System Uptime**: >99% operational availability
- **API Response Time**: <200ms average response time
- **Data Logging**: 100% transaction logging for monitoring

